@yesamer Yes what @karreiro said. I do this with Verification. For the errors/warnings/info messages I have an ID for each type that is just an enum. Then in the client side I have a Report Generator that gets a message based on the ID. If the message template needs variable, I have them in the message object.
In the example I produce HTML, but might as well just use the same for more simple i18n.
